Interface ByteIndexedContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:

    @Generated(date="2020-09-07T17:20:13+0200",
           value="KTypeIndexedContainer.java")
public interface ByteIndexedContainer
extends ByteCollection, java.util.RandomAccess
    An indexed container provides random access to elements based on an index. Indexes are zero-based.
